{"tid":2278073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有冇諗過民主本身就係一個左膠制度？","createTime":"2020-11-09T02:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T02:52:09.000Z","uid":33939,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"930472737a11e543b698ad0cfd68472dd032759b","tid":2278073,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:11:32.000Z","msg":"民主唔係淨係有票投，仲有係追求平等，人權，大愛哩啲嘢，尤其係行咗咁多年嘅民主制度。<br />\n<br />\n你唔好理美國啲人內心係咁真係咁美好定係偽善，但起碼晌道德嚟講哩啲門面嘢一定要做。即係好似我哋教細路仔唔好講大話咁，但現實中有邊個大人係唔講大話？<br />\n<br />\n而美國嘅教育就係會教佢哋哩啲價值觀，法例亦係會保障哩啲嘢。所以點解黑人俾人跪頸死咗，警察係被判有罪。"},{"pid":"b15b941564c1baeaaa40e8098ead9417067ab4f6","tid":2278073,"uid":34065,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:12:53.000Z","msg":"分清楚左 同左膠嘅分別先啦"},{"pid":"c4c0558e16cebbab5451fd6c83ad847219bb124d","tid":2278073,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:13:10.000Z","msg":"晌？"},{"pid":"d5fa3c750693a1e144d3229901cca075187c54da","tid":2278073,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:16:33.000Z","msg":"所以香港唔好有票投 港豬唔做左膠<br />\n點解香港人要爭取乜野民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da863ebcca43506b033aadce47bb04dff45e496","tid":2278073,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b15b941564c1baeaaa40e8098ead9417067ab4f6","tid":2278073,"uid":34065,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:12:53.000Z","msg":"分清楚左 同左膠嘅分別先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:26:44.000Z","msg":"點唔清楚？<br />\n我咪舉咗教細路仔講大話個例子"},{"pid":"52547d93b615497ecc44b8685d59bc29ed946b45","tid":2278073,"uid":282028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2da863ebcca43506b033aadce47bb04dff45e496","tid":2278073,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b15b941564c1baeaaa40e8098ead9417067ab4f6","tid":2278073,"uid":34065,